                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "attrs": {
            "align": null,
            "indent": 0
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "夜间下山路段危险！",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "attrs": {
            "align": null,
            "indent": 0
          },
          "content": [
            {
              "text": "立石公园通往车站的山路几乎没有路灯。看完黄昏后天会迅速全黑。",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "bulletList",
          "attrs": {
            "align": null,
            "indent": 0
          },
          "content": [
